As to Flicker, he's in the Predacon base waiting for the love of his 
life (and roommate, and you can fill in the blanks) to get back from 
her search-and-retrieval mission.

BTW, Phoenix isn't nearly so innocent as when Flicker rescued her.  
In case you haven't read all the important posts, I'll sum it up: her 
father Skyblaze restored her memory, and she learned she is actually 
a member of the Lumin, a pure-energy race with fantastic powers.  Her 
life-force was contained in the form of a transformer's spark, 
creating a bot with immense powers.  She is now starting to establish 
some measure of control over those powers.
